---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Our Values">
  <!-- Background wrapper with image -->
  <section 
    class="relative container-x py-14 md:py-20 bg-cover bg-center" 
    style="background-image: url('/only-jesus.jpg');"
  >
    <!-- Overlay to soften the background -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-white/85"></div>

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <!-- Mobile smaller (3xl), Desktop unchanged (4xl) -->
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold tracking-wide text-warmgray-900">
        Our Values
      </h1>

      <!-- Slogan under heading -->
      <!-- Mobile smaller (base), desktop keeps your large size via sm:3xl -->
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg sm:text-3xl text-center text-warmgray-800">
         <span class="text-brand-red">Come. See. Jesus</span>
      </p>

      <!-- Intro copy (split into two valid paragraphs) -->
      <!-- Mobile smaller (base), Desktop unchanged (md:2xl) -->
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-2xl text-warmgray-700">
        At The Life Place, our heartbeat is Jesus.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-2xl text-gray-700">
        Our values shape who we are and how we live together as His people.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Values grid -->
    <div class="relative z-10 mt-12 grid gap-6 md:gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 auto-rows-fr">
      <!-- 1 -->
      <article class="h-full rounded-xl border bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-5 md:p-7 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <!-- Mobile smaller title (xl), Desktop unchanged (2xl) -->
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-left">
          Hear the good news
        </h3>
        <!-- Body: mobile base, desktop lg -->
        <p class="text-xl md:text-lg text-warmgray-700">
          Just as Jesus taught that everything in the Bible was written about Him, so every time we open the Bible, we are invited to see and meet with Him. And when we see Jesus, we hear the good news.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-center text-warmgray-800">
          (Luke 24:47, John 1:19-35, 5:39, 46, 12:26-27, 13:3)
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- 2 -->
      <article class="h-full rounded-xl border bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-5 md:p-7 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-left">
          Diverse Community
        </h3>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-lg text-warmgray-800">
          Rooted in the good news, we celebrate every story, background, and culture—nations, tribes, peoples, and languages.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-center text-warmgray-800">
          (Acts 2:46–47; Ephesians 3; Romans 8:15; Galatians 4:6; Revelation 7:9)
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- 3 -->
      <article class="h-full rounded-xl border bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-5 md:p-7 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-left">
          Extravagant Generosity
        </h3>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-lg text-warmgray-700">
          Made rich by what Jesus has done, we are generous and share in all things.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-center text-warmgray-500">
          (Acts 2:45; 4:35; 2 Corinthians 8:2–4, 9, 16–24; 9:1–15)
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- 4 -->
      <article class="h-full rounded-xl border bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-5 md:p-7 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition lg:col-start-1 lg:row-start-2">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-left">
          Graceful Compassion
        </h3>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-lg text-warmgray-700">
          The good news moves us beyond our comforts to show grace to the widowed, the orphan,
          the poor, the imprisoned, and the immigrant.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-center text-warmgray-500">
          (Deut 10:18; 14:29; 16:11; 24:17,19–21; Matt 25:35–36; Acts 6:1–3; Gal 2:9; James 1:27; 2:14–17; Jude 9)
        </p>
      </article>

      <!-- 5 -->
      <article class="h-full rounded-xl border bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm p-5 md:p-7 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition lg:col-start-3 lg:row-start-2">
        <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-left">
          Go live the story
        </h3>
        <!-- fixed malformed class attribute; mobile base, desktop lg -->
        <p class="text-xl md:text-lg text-warmgray-700">
          In our homes, workplaces, and city, we embody the good news and engage the culture with grace and courage—not to condemn, but to redeem.
        </p>
        <!-- fixed 'text-m' to 'text-sm' -->
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-center text-warmgray-500">
          (John 17:15–19; Acts 17:16–34; 1 Corinthians 9:19–22)
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Scripture footer -->
  <div class="border-t mt-12 md:mt-16 pt-8 md:pt-10 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Mobile slightly smaller, desktop unchanged -->
    <blockquote class="text-lg md:text-xl italic text-gray-800">
      “I came that they may have and enjoy life and have it in abundance (to the full, till it overflows)”
    </blockquote>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm md:text-base text-warmgray-600">John 10:10 AMP</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
